These are the files I have coded so far for a wordpress theme satisfying the following requirements:
- mobile-friendly and mobile-responsive
- different content displayed for desktop and mobile users
- fully compatible with plugins from the wordpress ecosystem
- compatible with popular SEO plugins like yoast
- fixed header but not fixed footer for each page
- a menu is in the header, with menu items and sub-items. Each of the menu items and sub-items change cover when the user hovers over the text. Each menu item links to a separate page (to be customized later).
- CSS functionality replaces JavaScript whenever possible

Check my code for mistakes, misplaced code blocks, and failure to satisfying any of the above requirements.

---

FILE: style.css

```css

/* Reset some default styles */
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  line-height: 1.6;
  background-color: #f9f9f9;
  color: #333;
}

header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  background-color: #0044cc;
  padding: 10px;
}

header img.logo {
  height: 50px;
  margin-right: 20px;
}

.menu-toggle-checkbox {
  display: none;
}

.menu-toggle-label {
  display: none;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  color: white;
  font-size: 2rem;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.menu {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
}

.menu ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
}

.menu-item {
  position: relative;
}

.menu-item a {
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s;
}

.menu-item a:hover {
  color: #ffcc00;
}

.has-submenu .submenu {
  display: none;
  position: absolute;
  top: 100%;
  left: 0;
  background-color: #0044cc;
  padding: 10px;
  list-style: none;
}

.has-submenu:hover .submenu {
  display: block;
}

.submenu li {
  margin: 5px 0;
}

.submenu a {
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s;
}

.submenu a:hover {
  color: #ffcc00;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .menu {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    background-color: #0044cc;
    padding: 10px;
  }

  .menu ul {
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .menu-toggle-label {
    display: block;
  }

  .menu-toggle-checkbox:checked + .menu-toggle-label + .menu {
    display: flex;
  }

  .menu-item.has-submenu:hover .submenu {
    display: block;
  }

  .desktop-only {
    display: none;
  }

  .mobile-only {
    display: block;
  }
}

@media (min-width: 769px) {
  .mobile-only {
    display: none;
  }

  .desktop-only {
    display: block;
  }
}

.content-area {
  padding: 20px;
}
   ```

